Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,含羞草鸡尾酒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,663)\fs32}Sangria
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,桑格利亚汽酒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都没点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们给大家点的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(835,663)\fs32}Cocktail
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,与你们形象相符合的鸡尾酒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,与我们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,形象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,然后这是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(795,663)\fs32}No alcohol Cocktail
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,符合坂本形象的无酒精鸡尾酒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,663)\fs32}Merry Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下  坂本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在社交礼仪当中  这种饮品是要一口气喝完的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒  坂本来唱首歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,还没听过你唱歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,想听  想听
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,坂本唱的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,发声要洪亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好  上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,让你喝的鸡尾酒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是纯度100%的可乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\be5\c&H252A2A&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(640,550)}作曲/舒伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,让人兴奋不已啊
